docs.text: Example Hello! This is how code can be inserted: { "SimulationState" : "running", "Name" : "Name of the simulation", "Description" : "Longer description about the simulation" } This thing supports even tables: Field Type Multiplicity Explanation All fields from AbstractMessage Fields from the "abstract base class" SimulationState String 1 (REQUIRED) Simulation state, either: "running" or "stopped" Name String 0..1 (OPTIONAL) A human friendly name for the simulation. Description String 0..1 (OPTIONAL) A longer description of the simulation run meant for humans.
